<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to the Channel!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .signature b {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .signature a {
            margin-right: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        Hi ${ownerName},
        <p>We’re writing to confirm that your profile and your pet’s details have been successfully removed from <b>Petistaan</b>.</p>
        <div class="signature">
            <b>Thanks and Regards</b>
            Team Petistaan
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            If you did not subscribed or received this email by mistake, please ignore it.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>